<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Video Call Invitation - Ocean Holidays</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote {
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        table, td {
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
        }
        img {
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
        }

        /* Base styles */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100% !important;
            min-width: 100%;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        /* Container */
        .email-container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        /* Header with logo */
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7c245 0%, #e35649 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .email-header p {
            margin: 15px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* Content */
        .email-content {
            padding: 45px 40px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .email-content h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 0 0 25px 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }

        .email-content p {
            margin: 0 0 18px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #34495e;
        }

        .email-content ul {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .email-content li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #34495e;
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .email-content li:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #f7c245;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Main CTA Button */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7c245 0%, #e35649 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 17px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(247, 194, 69, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(247, 194, 69, 0.6);
        }

        .button-center {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }

        /* Info boxes */
        .info-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9e6 0%, #ffeaa7 20%);
            border-left: 5px solid #f7c245;
            padding: 20px 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(247, 194, 69, 0.2);
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .info-box p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        /* Features section */
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-top: 3px solid #f7c245;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-item .icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: block;
        }

        .feature-item h4 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .feature-item p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* URL box */
        .url-box {
            word-break: break-all;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid #f7c245;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Divider */
        .divider {
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7c245 0%, #e35649 100%);
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .email-footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .email-footer p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #bdc3c7;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .email-footer .company-info {
            color: #f7c245;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        /* Support section */
        .support-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #bbdefb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #e35649;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .support-box h3 {
            color: #e35649;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .support-box p {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .support-link {
            color: #e35649 !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .support-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media screen and (max-width: 650px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 95% !important;
                margin: 10px auto !important;
                border-radius: 8px !important;
            }
            
            .email-header,
            .email-content,
            .email-footer {
                padding: 25px 20px !important;
            }

            .email-header h1 {
                font-size: 26px !important;
            }

            .logo {
                max-width: 150px !important;
            }

            .button {
                display: block !important;
                width: 100% !important;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                padding: 16px 20px !important;
                font-size: 16px !important;
            }

            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
                gap: 15px !important;
            }

            .email-content h2 {
                font-size: 22px !important;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .email-content {
                padding: 20px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .email-header {
                padding: 25px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .logo {
                max-width: 120px !important;
                padding: 8px 15px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://www.ocean-holidays.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/oh-logo.png" alt="Ocean Holidays" class="logo">
            <h1>🎥 Video Call Invitation</h1>
            <p>You've been invited to join a personalized video consultation</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-content">
            <h2>Dear {{customerName}},</h2>
            
            <p>We're excited to invite you to a personalized video consultation with our travel experts. This is your opportunity to discuss your dream holiday in detail and receive tailored recommendations just for you.</p>
            
            <div class="button-center">
                <a href="{{joinUrl}}" class="button">Join Your Consultation</a>
            </div>

            {{#if sessionDetails}}
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>📋 Session Details</h3>
                {{#if sessionDetails.date}}
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{sessionDetails.date}}</p>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if sessionDetails.time}}
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{sessionDetails.time}}</p>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if sessionDetails.duration}}
                <p><strong>Expected Duration:</strong> {{sessionDetails.duration}}</p>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if sessionDetails.agenda}}
                <p><strong>Discussion Topics:</strong> {{sessionDetails.agenda}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <h2>🌟 What Makes This Special</h2>
            
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="icon">🎯</span>
                    <h4>Personalized Service</h4>
                    <p>Tailored recommendations based on your preferences and budget</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="icon">🗺️</span>
                    <h4>Expert Knowledge</h4>
                    <p>Insights from our experienced travel consultants</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="icon">💎</span>
                    <h4>Exclusive Deals</h4>
                    <p>Access to special offers and packages not available online</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="icon">🤝</span>
                    <h4>No Pressure</h4>
                    <p>Friendly consultation with no obligation to book</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <h2>�️ Your Experience Includes</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>HD video and crystal-clear audio quality</li>
                <li>Screen sharing for viewing destinations and accommodations</li>
                <li>Interactive holiday package presentations</li>
                <li>Real-time price comparisons and availability checks</li>
                <li>Secure and private consultation environment</li>
                {{#if additionalFeatures}}
                {{#each additionalFeatures}}
                <li>{{this}}</li>
                {{/each}}
                {{/if}}
            </ul>

            <h2>⚙️ Technical Requirements</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Edge recommended)</li>
                <li>Camera and microphone access (for the best experience)</li>
                <li>Stable internet connection</li>
                <li>No software download required - works directly in your browser</li>
                {{#if technicalRequirements}}
                {{#each technicalRequirements}}
                <li>{{this}}</li>
                {{/each}}
                {{/if}}
            </ul>

            {{#if instructions}}
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>📝 Special Instructions</h3>
                <p>{{instructions}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="support-box">
                <h3>🆘 Need Technical Support?</h3>
                <p>If you experience any issues joining the call, please don't hesitate to contact us:</p>
                <p>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:{{#if supportContact}}{{supportContact}}{{else}}support@ocean-holidays.co.uk{{/if}}" class="support-link">{{#if supportContact}}{{supportContact}}{{else}}support@ocean-holidays.co.uk{{/if}}</a></p>
                <p>📞 Phone: +44 (0) 208 371 7777</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Alternative Access:</strong> If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link directly into your browser:</p>
            <div class="url-box">{{joinUrl}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p class="company-info">Ocean Holidays - Your Trusted Travel Partner</p>
            <p>This consultation invitation is valid for {{#if validityPeriod}}{{validityPeriod}}{{else}}7 days{{/if}}.</p>
            <p>We're here to help you create unforgettable memories with personalized travel experiences.</p>
            <p>🌐 Website: <a href="https://www.ocean-holidays.co.uk" style="color: #f7c245; text-decoration: none;">www.ocean-holidays.co.uk</a></p>
            <p>📍 Address: Ocean House, 132-140 High Road, Loughton, Essex, IG10 4BE</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{#if companyName}}{{companyName}}{{else}}Ocean Holidays{{/if}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px; color: #95a5a6;">
                This email was sent because you requested a consultation with Ocean Holidays. 
                If you believe this was sent in error, please contact us at support@ocean-holidays.co.uk
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>